    <p>Bernanke said we are recovering, and QE is good for Main Street.</p>
<p>Bernanke also said that he doesn't understand gold prices, and that CB's buy it because of tradition.</p>
<p>Since I see no recovery, and see Main Street suffering bigtime, I have to assume that Bernanke is a liar who understands gold prices and knows it is much more valuable than just tradition.</p>
<p>I buy PM's regularly because of him.</p>
<p>Had he not been a habitual liar, I might think otherwise.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
